Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拥有　不想忘却的回忆么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:59.50,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
