Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:09.39,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, with my little wings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:15.56,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:21.81,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:28.49,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:35.12,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:40.83,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:48.38,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it up, here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:53.93,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Be alive, take it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:57.18,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise to find, yes I will
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:03.73,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining wings filled with wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:06.69,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:10.03,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:16.95,EDEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, so I believe
